    {
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Step through each colour:\n  R: ing1=R- (ing1 R?: (sign undetermined)), ing3=R+ (ing3 R?: (sign undetermined))\n      \u2192 opposite signs \u2192 skip.\n  G: ing1=G- (ing1 G?: (sign undetermined)), ing3=G+ (ing3 G?: (sign undetermined))\n      \u2192 opposite signs \u2192 skip.\n  B: ing1=B+ (ing1 has B+), ing3=B+ (ing3 has B+)\n      \u2192 SAME sign + \u2192 B+ resolves."
    },
